pert%20shared%20the%20healthy%2C%20filling%20lunch%20he%20eats%20most%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Will%20Bulsiewicz%2C%20a%20gastroenterologist%20and%20the%20US%20Medical%20Director%20of%20the%20nutrition%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EZOE%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20eats%20bean%20chili%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmoothie-recipe-gut-health-gastroenterologist-breakfast-daily-drink-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeasy%20breakfast%20smoothie%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20drinks%20each%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20typical%20lunch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flazy-girl-lunch-ideas-recipes-fat-loss-muscle-gain-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehardy%20lunch%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sticks%20to%20the%20ribs%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20satisfying%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20making%20me%20feel%20full%20(which%20it%20does)%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20make%20it%20really%20spicy%2C%20which%20I%20love.%E2%80%9D%20Not%20only%20is%20it%20filling%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20good%20for%20gut%20health%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecause%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBulsiewicz%20has%20bean%20chili%2C%20farro%2C%20and%20sourdough%20bread%20for%20lunch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20week%2C%20Bulsiewicz%20makes%20a%20large%20batch%20of%20bean%20chili%20in%20a%20pressure%20cooker%20and%20adds%20hot%20sauce%20to%20make%20it%20extra%20spicy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChili%20contains%20a%20variety%20of%20beans%20and%20vegetables%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20great%20source%20of%20nutrients%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fiber%2C%20which%20is%20important%20for%20digestion%20and%20regulating%20blood%20sugar%20spikes%2C%20Bulsiewicz%20said.%20Beans%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ffiber-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econtain%20a%20lot%20of%20fiber%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBulsiewicz%20eats%20his%20chili%20with%20farro%2C%20a%20whole%20grain%2C%20seasoned%20with%20turmeric%20and%20black%20pepper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTurmeric%20is%20great%20for%20our%20gut%20microbes%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-inflammatory-foods-to-help-prevent-chronic-inflammation-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eanti-inflammatory%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Research%20suggests%20that%20black%20pepper%20can%20help%20the%20body%20absorb%20turmeric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20has%20any%20in%20the%20house%2C%20he%20will%20also%20eat%20some%20sourdough%20bread%20with%20his%20chili%20and%20farro.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSourdough%20is%20delicious%20and%20makes%20me%20very%20happy.%20I%20might%20even%20dip%20it%20in%20some%20extra%20virgin%20olive%20oil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fis-sourdough-bread-healthy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESourdough%20is%20considered%20healthier%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20white%20or%20wheat%20bread%2C%20because%20the%20body%20can%20absorb%20more%20nutrients%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKombucha%20at%20lunch%20provides%20%3Cstrong%3Ea%20source%20of%20fermented%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBulsiewicz%20often%20pairs%20his%20chili%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fkombucha-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ekombucha%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20fermented%20tea%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20kombucha%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20miracle%20drink%2C%20as%20some%20would%20have%20you%20believe%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20can%20make%20better%20and%20worse%20choices%20with%20food%2C%20always%2C%20and%20drinking%20a%20kombucha%20is%20better%20than%20drinking%20Diet%20Coke%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKombucha%20is%20a%20fermented%20food%2C%20and%20research%20suggests%20it%20can%20help%20limit%20inflammation%2C%20improve%20gut%20health%20by%20feeding%20good%20bacteria%2C%20and%20strengthen%20the%20immune%20system%20thanks%20to%20the%20B%20vitamins%20it%20contains%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Cleveland%20Clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBulsiewicz%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20fermented%20foods%20are%20one%20of%20the%20food%20types%20he%20recommends%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffoods-for-gut-health-fgoals-gastroenterologist-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20gut%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-healthy-lunch-recipe-gastroenterologist-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708765262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ccb41b94aa8ee8e84b26fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-healthy-lunch-recipe-gastroenterologist-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr.%20Will%20Bulsiewicz's%20gut-healthy%20chili%2C%20which%20he%20pairs%20with%20kombucha%2C%20is%20packed%20full%20of%20fiber.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22skenny%40businessinsider.com%20(Serafina%20Kenny)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-healthy-lunch-recipe-gastroenterologist-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trial%20over%20Black%20transgender%20woman's%20death%20in%20rural%20South%20Carolina%20focuses%20on%20secret%20relationship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708765167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107964934%2Cimgsize-561447.cms%22%2C%22or