C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20repeal%20the%20personal%20law%20governing%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20among%20Muslims%20in%20a%20big%20push%20towards%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(ICC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUCC%20refers%20to%20a%20common%20set%20of%20laws%20applicable%20to%20all%20Indian%20citizens%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20religion%20in%20dealing%20with%20personal%20matters%20like%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20and%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Uttarakhand%20becoming%20the%20first%20state%20to%20pass%20a%20UCC%20law%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Assam%20has%20been%20hinting%20at%20bringing%20a%20similar%20law.%20There's%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20government%20may%20introduce%20a%20UCC%20bill%20during%20the%20Budget%20session%20that%20ends%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20step%20towards%20this%2C%20Assam%20Minister%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%20said%20on%20Friday%20the%20cabinet%20has%20decided%20to%20repeal%20the%20Muslim%20Marriage%20and%20Divorce%20Registration%20Act.%20The%20government%20now%20wants%20to%20bring%20all%20such%20matters%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20said%20Mr%20Baruah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20will%20change%20after%20the%20law%20is%20repealed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFormalise%20Registration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20law%20allows%20voluntary%20registration%20of%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20among%20Muslims.%20It%20is%20not%20mandatory%20under%20the%20law%20to%20register%20such%20instances.%20The%20registration%20machinery%20too%20is%20informal%20which%20provides%20for%20a%20scope%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20extant%20norms%2C%20said%20Mr%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20More%20Muslim%20Registrars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20registrars%20holding%20licenses%20to%20register%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20in%20the%20community%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20register%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20once%20the%20law%20is%20repealed.%20Mr%20Baruah%20has%20said%2094%20Muslim%20registrars%2C%20who%20have%20been%20registering%20marriages%20under%20the%20law%2C%20will%20be%20given%20a%20one-time%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustody%20of%20Registration%20Records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20law%20is%20scrapped%2C%20the%20district%20commissioners%20and%20district%20registrars%20will%20have%20the%20%26quot%3Bcustody%20of%20registration%20records%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Sarma.%20The%20registrations%20will%20be%20done%20under%20the%20supervision%20and%20control%20of%20the%20Assam%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Registration.%20Currently%2C%20the%2094%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registrars%20hold%20the%20authority%20to%20be%20the%20custodians%20of%20such%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrevent%20Child%20Marriages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20law%20allows%20marriages%20to%20be%20registered%20even%20if%20the%20bride%20and%20the%20groom%20have%20not%20reached%20the%20legal%20age%20of%2018%20and%2021.%20The%20scrapping%20of%20the%20law%20will%20mark%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20Assam%2C%20said%20Mr%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708763400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2F1346v45g_himanta-biswa-sarma-pti_625x300_11_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-changes-after-assam-scraps-muslim-marriage-registration-law-5118231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Assam%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20repeal%20the%20personal%20law%20governing%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20among%20Muslims%20in%20a%20big%20push%20towards%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(ICC).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-changes-after-assam-scraps-muslim-marriage-registration-law-5118231%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-changes-after-assam-scraps-muslim-marriage-registration-law-5118231%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-changes-after-assam-scraps-muslim-marriage-registration-law-5118231%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20and%20AAP%20Seal%20Seat-Sharing%20Deal%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%2C%20but%20to%20Go%20Solo%20in%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24135423%2Fimage-1863.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20on%20Saturday%20(February%2024)%20ended%20months%20of%20speculation%20surrounding%20its%20fate%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20announced%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Chandigarh%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20while%20deciding%20to%20fight%20solo%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20there%20are%20seven%20seats%20on%20which%20AAP%20will%20fight%20on%20four%20seats.%20These%20are%20New%20Delhi%2C%20West%20Delhi%2C%20South%20Delhi%2C%20and%20East%20Delhi.%20Congress%20will%20fight%20on%20three%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20Chandni%20Chowk%2C%20North%20East%2C%20and%20North%20West%2C%E2%80%9D%20announced%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20National%20Alliance%20Committee%20convenor%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20at%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20its%2026%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Congress%20will%20contest%2024%2C%20while%20AAP%20will%20contest%20two%2C%20including%20Bharuch%20and%20Bhavnagar.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20which%20has%2010%20seats%2C%20Congress%20will%20fight%20on%20the%20nine%20seats%2C%20and%20AAP%20will%20fight%20on%20one%2C%20which%20is%20Kurukshetra.%20Long%20rounds%20of%20talks%20were%20held%20on%20the%20Chandigarh%20seat.%20It%20was%20finally%20decided%20that%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20will%20contest%20this%20seat.%20Detailed%20discussions%20also%20took%20place%20regarding%20Goa%2C%20and%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20both%20seats%20will%20be%20fought%20by%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Congress%20chief%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%2C%20former%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Deepak%20Babaria%2C%20AAP%20MLAs%20Atishi%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%20and%20AAP%20MP%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20were%20present%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20parties%20have%20opted%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20separately%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20AAP%20holds%20power%20and%20Congress%20serves%20as%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20parties%20(AAP%20and%20Congress)%20have%20mutually%20agreed%20to%20contest%20the%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20elections%20in%20Punjab%20separately%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20go%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-aap-to-go-solo-in-punjab-major-setback-for-india%2Farticleshow%2F107580814.cms%5C%22%3Esolo%20and%20fight%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20announcement%20comes%20after%20AAP%20had%20alleged%2C%20in%20separate%20press%20conferences%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%2C%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-bjp-congress-arrest%5C%22%3Eplanning%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20if%20the%20party%20proceeds%20with%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasnik%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20AAP%20or%20Kejriwal%20who%20are%20facing%20such%20pressure%20tactics%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20AAP%20or%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20kind%20of%20circumstances%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20created%20today%20in%20the%20country%20is%20a%20challenge%20to%20democracy.%20Using%20CBI%2C%20ED%2C%20Income%20Tax%20on%20everyone%20to%20put%20pressure%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20politics%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%2C%20which%20is%20dangerous%20for%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20and%20not%20just%20Congress%20and%20AAP%2C%20but%20the%20people%20of%20India%20will%20fight%20against%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20were%20shrouded%20in%20speculation%20for%20months.%20The%20final%20shape%20to%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20came%20only%20weeks%20after%20AAP%20threw%20the%20gauntlet%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-throws-down-gauntlet-to-congress-seat-sharing-delay%5C%22%3Eonly%20one%20seat%20to%20the%20Congress%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20capital%20while%20saying%20it%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cdeserve%20a%20single%20seat%20on%20merit%E2%80%9D.%20While%20the%20national%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20admitted%20to%20a%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20its%20Delhi%20unit%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cenergised%E2%80%9D%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20set%20aside%20their%20political%20interests%20and%20have%20come%20together%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintention%20of%20this%20alliance%20is%20that%20it%20is%20the%20country%20which%20is%20importa