2%3A%22Assam%20Repeals%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Act%3B%20BJP%20Cites%20Intent%20to%20Implement%20UCC%20in%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08144104%2FGFlamxXa0AAQFxW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Assam%20government%20on%20Friday%20(February%2023)%20approved%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Assam%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Registration%20Act%2C%201935%2C%20in%20what%20an%20Assam%20minister%20termed%20as%20a%20significant%20step%20forward%20towards%20implementing%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20claimed%20that%20the%20decision%20will%20help%20the%20government%20prevent%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20state%2C%20his%20cabinet%20minister%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%20laid%20out%20a%20larger%20motivation%20behind%20the%20move%2C%20that%20is%20to%20implement%20the%20UCC%20in%20Assam.%20Baruah%20also%20said%20that%20the%20existing%20law%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccolonial%20Act%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%2C%20Sarma%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2023%2C%20the%20Assam%20cabinet%20made%20a%20significant%20decision%20to%20repeal%20the%20age-old%20Assam%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Registration%20Act.%20This%20act%20contained%20provisions%20allowing%20marriage%20registration%20even%20if%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20had%20not%20reached%20the%20legal%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2021%2C%20as%20required%20by%20the%20law.%20This%20move%20marks%20another%20significant%20step%20towards%20prohibiting%20child%20marriages%20in%20Assam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhimanta-chartered-flights-helicopter-assam-assembly%5C%22%3ERs%2058%2C23%2C07%2C104%3A%20Public%20Money%20Spent%20on%20CM%20Himanta%2C%20Other%20VIPs%E2%80%99%20Air%20Travel%2C%20According%20to%20Assam%20Govt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarma%20has%20been%20leading%20a%20campaign%20against%20child%20marriages%2C%20but%20his%20critics%20claim%20that%20the%20campaign%20has%20mostly%20targeted%20Muslim%20families%20of%20the%20state%20and%20has%20visible%20communal%20undertones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20Sarma%20said%20that%20the%20need%20to%20repeal%20the%20Act%20arose%20because%20it%20does%20not%20require%20mandatory%20registration%20of%20marriages%20and%20divorces%2C%20and%20is%20only%20voluntary%2C%20leaving%20much%20scope%20for%20%E2%80%9Cnon-compliance%20of%20norms%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20provisions%20of%20the%20act%2C%20there%20remains%20scope%20for%20registering%20marriages%20of%20intended%20persons%20below%2021%20years%20(for%20males)%20and%2018%20years%20(for%20females)%20and%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20monitoring%20for%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20state%20government%20told%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-will-change-after-repeal-of-assam-muslim-marriage-divorce-registration-law-101708743416744.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Act%20will%20allow%20the%20Assam%20government%E2%80%99s%20district%20commissioners%20and%20district%20registrars%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20custody%20of%20registration%20records%20held%20by%2094%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registrars%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Registrars%20have%20been%20promised%20a%20one-time%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20their%20rehabilitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E