2%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20claims%20criminal%20indictments%20boosted%20support%20among%20black%20voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708759123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107962563%2Cimgsize-700001.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-draws-parallel-between-his-criminal-indictments-and-historic-anti-black-prejudice%2Farticleshow%2F107961322.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107961322.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-draws-parallel-between-his-criminal-indictments-and-historic-anti-black-prejudice%2Farticleshow%2F107961322.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-draws-parallel-between-his-criminal-indictments-and-historic-anti-black-prejudice%2Famp_articleshow%2F107961322.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-draws-parallel-between-his-criminal-indictments-and-historic-anti-black-prejudice%2Famp_articleshow%2F107961322.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Action%20To%20Be%20Taken%20Against%20Colleges%20Forcing%20Students%20To%20Take%20Hostels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20(NMC)%20has%20issued%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmc.org.in%2FMCIRest%2Fopen%2FgetDocument%3Fpath%3D%2FDocuments%2FPublic%2FPortal%2FLatestNews%2FPress%2520Release-2.pdf%5C%22%3Eadvisory%20for%20medical%20colleges%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20Regulation%205.6%20of%20the%20Post%20Graduate%20Medical%20Education%20Regulation%20(PGMER)%2C%202023.%20The%20regulation%20mandates%20that%20while%20colleges%20have%20the%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20suitable%20residential%20accommodation%20to%20postgraduate%20students%2C%20it%20is%20not%20compulsory%20for%20students%20to%20reside%20in%20%C2%A0these%20accommodations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20body%20has%20released%20the%20notification%20again%20as%20despite%20previous%20warnings%2C%20many%20colleges%20were%20forcing%20students%20to%20take%20the%20hostel%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20notification%20released%20by%20the%20NMC%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20recent%20public%20notice%20dated%20February%208%2C%202024%2C%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20has%20addressed%20concerns%20regarding%20hostel%20accommodation%20for%20post%20graduate%20medical%20students.%20The%20notice%20highlights%20Regulation%205.6%20of%20the%20Post%20Graduate%20Medical%20Education%20Regulation%20(PGMER)%2C%202023%2C%20which%20mandates%20colleges%20to%20provide%20suitable%20residential%20accommodation%20to%20post-graduate%20students.%20However%2C%20it%20emphasises%20that%20it%20is%20not%20obligatory%20for%20the%20students%20to%20reside%20in%20these%20hostels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20underscores%20that%20previous%20regulations%2C%20such%20as%20the%20PGMER%2C%202000%2C%20did%20not%20mandate%20the%20compulsory%20stay%20of%20postgraduate%20medical%20students%20in%20college%20provided%20hostels%2C%20the%20notification%20added.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20clear%20directive%2C%20the%20NMC%20has%20received%20numerous%20complaints%20from%20postgraduate%20students%20alleging%20coercion%20by%20medical%20colleges%2Finstitutions%20to%20stay%20in%20designated%20hostels%2C%20accompanied%20by%20hefty%20charges.%20Such%20actions%20are%20deemed%20violations%20of%20Regulation%205.6%20of%20the%20PGMER%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20grievances%2C%20the%20NMC%20has%20directed%20all%20medical%20colleges%20an