%20always%20a%20tough%C2%A0ask%2C%20with%20no%20one%20in%20any%20doubt%20that%20it%20is%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20that%20is%20best%20poised%20to%20keep%20the%20saffron%20party%C2%A0in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20does%20it%20seem%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20formal%20tie-up%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%C2%A0is%20set%20to%20damage%20its%20prospects%20to%20any%20countable%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20possible%20that%20many%20voters%20not%20formally%20aligned%20with%20the%20ruling%20TMC%20but%20inimical%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20may%20cross%20over%20to%20it%20on%20their%20own%20sensible%20volition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Bihar%2C%20it%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20the%20case%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20trudge%20back%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20is%20likely%20to%20boost%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20to%20any%20considerable%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20revulsion%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20against%20endless%2C%20unprincipled%20tumbles%20at%20the%20top%20may%20have%20reached%20a%20tipping%20point%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%2C%20significantly%2C%20employment%20afforded%20to%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20teachers%20recently%C2%A0is%20generally%20recognised%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2FNov%2F02%2Fnitish-locks-horns-with-rjd-ministers-over-credit-for-teachers-recruitment-2629293.html%5C%22%3ETejaswi-RJD%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal)%20accomplishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%203%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahagathbandhan%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealliance%20is%20due%20to%20make%20a%20joint%20public%20appearance%20at%20a%20rally%20where%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20other%20left%20leaders%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist%E2%80%93Leninist)%2C%20an