.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68384402%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68384402.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68384402.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Why%20Name%20Animals%20After%20Gods%2C%20Historical%20Figures%3F'%20Asks%20Kolkata%20HC%2C%20Suggests%20Changing%20Lions'%20Names%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17121846%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-10.43.15-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20hearing%20the%20case%20concerning%20lions%20named%20%E2%80%98Akbar%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Sita%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20directed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fcalcutta-high-court%2Fcalcutta-high-court-directs-vhps-plea-against-lioness-named-sita-to-be-reclassified-as-pil-state-submits-naming-took-place-at-tripura-zoo-250197%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Ereclassification%20of%20the%20plea%20submitted%20by%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%3C%2Fa%3E%20(VHP)%20as%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVHP%20had%20moved%20the%20circuit%20bench%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20high%20court%20against%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20of%20two%20lions%20named%20%E2%80%98Sita%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20brought%20to%20West%20Bengal%20from%20Tripura%20%E2%80%93%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20companion%20to%20the%20lion%20named%20%E2%80%98Akbar%E2%80%99%20as%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%5C%22%3Ehurt%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20advocate%20general%20(AAG)%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20lions%20had%20been%20named%20in%20Tripura%20and%20that%20it%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Tripura%20Zoo%20authorities%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fcalcutta-high-court%2Fcalcutta-high-court-directs-vhps-plea-against-lioness-named-sita-to-be-reclassified-as-pil-state-submits-naming-took-place-at-tripura-zoo-250197%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhattacharya%20remarked%20that%20this%20controversy%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20has%20given%20this%20name%3F%20Causing%20controversy%3F%20I%20was%20thinking%20whether%20any%20animal%20can%20be%20given%20a%20name%20after%20a%20god%2C%20mythological%20hero%2C%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20or%20Nobel%20laureate.%20You%20are%20a%20welfare%20state%20and%20it%20is%20a%20secular%20state.%20Why%20should%20you%20draw%20controversy%20by%20naming%20a%20lion%20after%20Sita%20and%20Akbar%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20Sita%2C%20but%20I%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20the%20naming%20of%20a%20lion%2C%20Akbar.%20He%20was%20a%20very%20efficient%20and%20noble%20Mughal%20emperor.%20Very%20successful%20and%20secular%20Mughal%20emperor.%20If%20it%20is%20already%20named%2C%20the%20state%20authority%20should%20shun%20it%20and%20avoid%20it.%20West%20Bengal%20should%20have%20challenged%20the%20names%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20concerns%20about%20potential%20religious%20controversies%2C%20the%20Bench%20urged%20the%20state%20to%20consider%20renaming%20the%20lioness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20proceedings%2C%20the%20court%20questioned%20the%20practice%20of%20naming%20animals%20after%20revered%20figures%2C%20gods%20and%20historical%20figures%20while%20stressing%20upon%20the%20need%20to%20avoid%20controversies%20related%20to%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAG%20said%20that%20the%20West%20Bengal%20authorities%20were%20considering%20renaming%20the%20lions%20due%20to%20the%20controversy%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98backlash%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20the%20court%20released%20the%20matter%2C%20granting%20the%20petitioners%20the%20liberty%20to%20amend%20their%20pleadings%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20PIL.%20The%20registry%20was%20directed%20to%20re-number%20and%20place%20the%20case%20before%20the%20appropriate%20bench%20specialising%20in%20PILs%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708703994000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17121846%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-10.43.15-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-name-animals-after-gods-historical-figures-asks-kolkata-hc-suggests-changing-lions-names%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAG%20said%20that%20the%20West%20Bengal%20authorities%20were%20considering%20renaming%20the%20lions%20due%20to%20the%20controversy%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98backlash%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-name-animals-after-gods-historical-figures-asks-kolkata-hc-suggests-changing-lions-names%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20years%20on%20since%20Russia's%20invasion%20but%20Ukraine%20is%20still%20in%20the%20fight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708702560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F1600x900%2F2372402230590568907_6466409.png%3F20240223124834%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftwo-years-on-since-russias-invasion-but-ukraine-is-still-in-the-fight-13079210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20years%20on%20from%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20war%20is%20largely%20at%20a%20stalemate%20but%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy's%20troops%20face%20acute%20shortages%20of%20ammunition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftwo-years-on-since-russias-invasion-but-ukraine-is-still-in-the-fight-13079210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftwo-years-on-since-russias-invasion-but-ukraine-is-still-in-the-fight-13079210%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftwo-years-on-since-russias-invasion-but-ukraine-is-still-in-the-fight-13079210%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Poacher'%3A%20Richie%20Mehta's%20Series%20Is%20a%20Robust%20Reminder%20of%20the%20Good%20Fight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23194739%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-7.46.42-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20series%20%3Cem%3EPoacher%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Richie%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20keeping%20things%20grounded%20gets%20tested%20around%20halfway%20into%20the%20show.%20Based%20on%20a%20real-life%20case%20in%202015%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20successful%20ivory%20raid%20ever%2C%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20show%20builds%20up%20to%20the%20character%20of%20%E2%80%98Poonam%20Verma%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Delhi-based%20art%20dealer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20number%20of%20times%20we%20hear%20her%20name%20in%20the%20initial%20episodes%2C%20no%20one%20would%E2%80%99ve%20blamed%20Mehta%20for%20casting%20a%20more%20recognisable%20face.%20Instead%2C%20Mehta%20(and%20casting%20director%20Mukesh%20Chhabra)%20opt%20for%20Sapna%20Sand%20%E2%80%93%20who%20only%20recently%20appeared%20in%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EDunki%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2023)%20in%20a%20less-significant%20role%20and%20known%20for%20blending%20into%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDdEJtvzT7jc%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Poacher%20-%20Official%20Trailer%20%7C%20Prime%20Video%20India%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESand%E2%80%99s%20casting%20is%20a%20masterstroke%20for%20someone%20who%20operates%20from%20the%20shadows%2C%20hiding%20in%20plain%20sight%2C%20and%20looking%20unmistakably%20ordinary.%20But%20she%E2%80%99s%20more%20than%20capable%20at%20what%20she%20does%3B%20she%20plays%20Verma%20with%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20entitlement%2C%20hubris%20and%20stickiness%2C%20a%20popular%20combination%20among%20the%20affluent%20folks%20of%20South%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20main%20antagonists%20of%20the%20show%2C%20Sand%E2%80%99s%20character%20alternates%20between%20victim%2C%20negotiator%2C%20bully%20and%20gangster.%20She%E2%80%99s%20convincing%20when%20she%20says%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anything%2C%20but%20the%20facade%20breaks%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20her%20daughter%20might%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVerma%20is%20excellent%20at%20playing%20chess%20with%20her%20interrogators%2C%20trying%20to%20cut%20a%20deal%20with%20them%2C%20intimidating%20them%20and%20finally%20confessing%20to%20(some%20of)%20her%20sins.%20Tiny%20bits%20of%20information%20trickle%20out%20when%20she%20realises%20that%20cops%20won%E2%80%99t%20back%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20final%20two%20episodes%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3EPoacher%3C%2Fem%3E%20gains%20maximum%20momentum%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20when%20it%20enters%20(and%20then%20exits)%20a%20dingy%20East%20Delhi%20suburb.%20Mehta%2C%20who%20earlier%20made%20the%20dense%20%3Cem%3EDelhi%20Crime%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2019)%20%E2%80%93%20set%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202012%20Delhi%20gangrape%20%E2%80%93%20seems%20to%20have%20developed%20a%20liking%20for%20exacting%20procedurals.%20After%20chronicling%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20Mehta%20turns%20his%20gaze%20towards%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20forest%20department%20and%20cases%20of%20elephant%20poaching%20and%20ivory%20smuggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20terrorism%2C%20narcotics%2C%20child-trafficking%20%E2%80%93%20one%20might%20not%20take%20wildlife%20conservation%20as%20seriously%2C%20or%20look%20at%20poaching%20as%20something%20as%20sinister.%20However%2C%20Mehta%20insists%20(more%20than%20once)%20ivory%20smugglers%20are%20as%20dangerous%20and%20violent%20as%20any%20other%20criminal%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Yakuza%20(Japanese%20mafia)%20and%20Triads%20(Chinese%20organised%20crime%20syndicate).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPoacher%3C%2Fem%3E%20begins%20with%20a%20close-up%20of%20an%20elephant%20(it%E2%80%99s%20computer-generated%2C%20but%20to%20the%20credit%20of%20the%20VFX%20team%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20immediately%20apparent).%20We%E2%80%99re%20allowed%20to%20witness%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20creature%2C%20shortly%20after%20which%20they%E2%80%99re%20shot%20dead%20%E2%80%93%20bringing%20us%20front%20and%20centre%20to%20the%20beastliness%20of%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20forest%20watcher%20shows%20up%20at%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20forest%20department%2C%20and%20claims%20that%20he%20helped%20poach%2018%20elephants.%20Officially%2C%20no%20poaching%20has%20happened%20in%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20yet%20only%20after%20a%20whistleblower%20alerts%20them%20does%20the%20department%20swing%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMala%20(Nimisha%20Sajayan)%20and%20Alan%20(Roshan%20Mathew)%20are%20reassigned%20by%20the%20field%20director%20Neel%20Banerjee%20(Dibyendu%20Bhattacharya%2C%20finally%20given%20a%20role%20worth%20his%20busy%20presence)%2C%20to%20investigate%20the%20case%20of%20poaching%20and%20to%20track%20down%20the%20ivory%20smugglers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDelhi%20Crime%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20criticised%20for%20how%20it%20painted%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20a%20sympathetic%20light%2C%20something%20Mehta%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20into%20consideration%20while%20writing%20%3Cem%3EPoacher%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0because%20the%20show%20seems%20extremely%20distrusting%20of%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20keeps%20emphasising%20on%20how%20the%20operation%20needs%20to%20be%20tight%2C%20and%20people%20should%20be%20told%20about%20the%20developments%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98need%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20basis.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20fascinating%20sequence%20in%20episode%20two%2C%20when%20Alan%20explains%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstorytelling%E2%80%9D%20behind%20call%20data%20records%2C%20and%20how%20it%20helps%20them%20triangulate%20the%20position%20of%20a%20main%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20%3Cem%3EDelhi%20Crime%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20even%20here%20Mehta%20gets%20down%20and%20dirty%20into%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20broken%20system%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20law%20enforcement%20system.%20Shown%20to%20be%20operating%20from%20deep-seated%20corruption%2C%20Mehta%20makes%20sure%20to%20convey%20that%20such%20breakthroughs%20are%20the%20exception%20rather%20than%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20Vartika%20Chaturvedi%20in%20%3Cem%3EDelhi%20Crime%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mehta%20finds%20his%20protagonist%20in%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20world.%20Mala%20%E2%80%93%20an%20animal%20lover%2C%20tirelessly%20works%20for%20mother%20nature%20around%20her.%20The%20first%20scene%20sees%20her%20rebuking%20a%20subordinate%20for%20slacking%20at%20his%20watch%20tower%20and%20missing%20an%20important%20bit%20of%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20she%E2%80%99s%20recruited%20by%20Banerjee%2C%20Mala%20works%20fiercely%2C%20showing%20up%20at%20home%20only%20for%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20having%20her%20meals%20and%20bit-conversations%20with%20her%20mother%20about%20personal%20obligations%2C%20only%20to%20leave%20again.%20Sajayan%2C%20acclaimed%20for%20her%20work%20in%20Malayalam%20and%20Tamil%20films%2C%20brings%20intensity%20to%20her%20part.%20However%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20little%20individuality%20to%20her%2C%20which%20never%20quite%20lets%20the%20character%20breathe%20outside%20the%20genre%20conventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMala%E2%80%99s%20character%20is%20saddled%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98past%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20her%20father%20used%20to%20be%20a%20poacher%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20neatly%20tie%20the%20threads%20with%20why%20she%E2%80%99s%20so%20personally%20invested%20in%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20animals.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20narrative%20shortcut%2C%20like%20abetting%20a%20male%20cop%20with%20a%20drinking%20problem%20and%20marital%20discord%2C%20only%20to%20show%20his%20brilliance%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20Roshan%20Mathew%E2%80%99s%20Alan%20gets%20the%20more%20balanced%2C%20comprehensive%20domestic%20dynamic.%20Working%20as%20a%20computer%20programmer%20with%20a%20wildlife%20NGO%2C%20Alan%20also%20moonlights%20as%20a%20wildlife%20crime%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Alan%20shows%20up%20to%20his%20hometown%20only%20to%20head%20to%20his%20workplace%20even%20before%20telling%20his%20wife%20and%20son%20about%20his%20trip%20home.%20Time%20is%20of%20the%20essence%2C%20and%20Alan%20needs%20to%20balance%20his%20responsibility%20as%20a%20wildlife%20crime%20fighter%2C%20as%20much%20as%20a%20husband%2Ffather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMathew%20is%20excellent%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20show%20%E2%80%93%20as%20someone%20more%20comfortable%20in%20his%20office%20surroundings%2C%20but%20someone%20who%20shows%20nerves%20and%20is%20on%20his%20toes%20as%20a%20husband%2Ffather%20during%20social%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20thrilling%20sequence%2C%20when%20he%20takes%20off%20from%20a%20wedding%20celebration%20for%20an%20hour%20to%20attend%20a%20work%20meeting%2C%20without%20his%20wife%20noticing.%20It%20tells%20us%20what%20an%20all-consuming%20job%20this%20really%20is%2C%20everything%20else%20has%20to%20take%20a%20backseat%20each%20and%20every%20time.%20How%20does%20anyone%20keep%20a%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98normalcy%E2%80%99%20in%20such%20an%20orbit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3EPoacher%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Bhattacharya%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20Neel%20Banerjee%20is%20meticulous%2C%20watchful%2C%20passionate%2C%20foul-mouthed%2C%20eager%2C%20and%20funny%20all%20at%20once.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20running%20gag%20about%20him%20calling%20his%20highly-placed%20bureaucrat%20friends%20for%20favours%2C%20starting%20with%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20never%20asked%20anything%20of%20you%20till%20date%2C%20but%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhattacharya%2C%20who%20has%20rarely%20been%20afforded%20such%20a%20primary%20character%2C%20is%20relaxed%2C%20busy%2C%20efficient%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20making%20his%20movements%20seem%20almost%20instinctive.%20His%20character%20Banerjee%20is%20seen%20battling%20with%20a%20health%20condition%20%E2%80%93%20which%20feels%20like%20an%20affectation%20on%20an%20already%20solid%20character%20%E2%80%93%20but%20Bhattacharya%20brings%20an%20underlying%20pathos%20to%20the%20character.%20%E2%80%9CGo%2C%20work%20on%20your%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20Alan%20at%20one%20point%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20has%20even%20stopped%20asking%20me.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20worst.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPoacher%3C%2Fem%3E%20joins%20a%20small%20niche%20in%20Hindi%20cinema%20that%20seem%20to%20explore%20ecological%20issues%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20mainstream%20thriller%2C%20including%20Amit%20Masurkar%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ESherni%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2021)%20and%20Sameer%20Saxena%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2023).%20However%2C%20what%20remains%20encouraging%20about%20the%20show%20is%20how%20effortlessly%20it%20switches%20between%20Malayalam%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Bengali%20and%20English%2C%20almost%20like%20it%20was%20second%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%E2%80%99s%20cynicism%20with%20the%20state%20of%20the%20nation%20shows%20up%20in%20the%20series%E2%80%99%20staggering%20finale%2C%20including%20the%20horrors%20of%20mobs%20and%20a%20thrilling%20chase%20sequence%20where%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20become%20the%20prey%20of%20TV%20vultures.%20The%20creator%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20indulge%20his%20characters%E2%80%99%20victory%20lap%20for%20too%20long%2C%20instead%20cutting%20to%20a%20closed-door%20meeting%20in%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20office%20%E2%80%93%20taking%20place%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20their%20haul%20from%20the%20East%20Delhi%20safe%20house.%20Over%20here%2C%20Banerjee%20hands%20a%20list%20of%20all%20potential%20buyers%2C%20the%20roots%20of%20this%20barbaric%20industry%2C%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20here%20are%20politicians%2C%20power%20brokers%2C%20billionaire%20industrialists.%20The%20CBI%20official%20sighs%2C%20takes%20the%20list%20off%20their%20hands%20and%20gives%20them%20assurances.%20Banerjee%2C%20Mala%20and%20Alan%20know%20exactly%20what%20it%20means%20deflating%20their%20lifelong%20zeal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20look%20into%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20says.%20How%20often%20have%20we%20heard%20this%20lie%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPoacher%20is%20now%20streaming%20on%20Amazon%20Prime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708702198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23194739%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-7.46.42-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fpoacher-richie-mehtas-series-is-a-robust-reminder-of-the-good-fight%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mehta%E2%80%99s%20cynicism%20with%20the%20state%20of%20the%20nation%20shows%20up%20in%20the%20series'%20staggering%20finale%2C%20including%20the%20horrors%20of%20mobs%20and%20a%20thrilling%20chase%20sequence%20where%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20become%20the%20prey%20of%20TV%20vultures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fpoacher-richie-mehtas-series-is-a-robust-reminder-of-the-good-fight%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22McDonald's%