di%20heartland%20stronghold.%20It%20cannot%20improve%20its%20tally%20here.%20Its%20prospects%20are%20no%20better%20in%20the%20East%20and%20in%20the%20South%20than%20they%20were%20in%202019.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20have%20deteriorated%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20in%20the%20North-East%20with%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20first%20two%20polls%20and%20the%20fires%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20at%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20lose%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20seats.%20According%20to%20the%20data%20crunching%20site%20run%20by%20Ajay%20Prakash%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20Does%20This%20Data%20Say%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20total%20tally%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20down%20by%2040%20seats%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertain%20recent%20developments%20have%20not%20favoured%20the%20BJP%20either.%20Its%20insidious%20efforts%20came%20a%20cropper%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20where%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20retained%20its%20government%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20machinations%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20Raj%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20appears%20to%20have%20emerged%20stronger%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20defection.%20In%20Chandigarh%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20the%20mayoral%20elections%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20party%20stands%20fully%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20striking%20down%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20may%20not%20amount%20to%20much%20in%20real%20terms%20because%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20pocketed%20Rs%206%2C500%20crore%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20delay%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20deciding%20the%20case%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20big%20moral%20defeat%20for%20the%20government%2C%20exposing%20once%20again%20the%20unconstitutional%20means%20it%20adopts%20to%20win%20elections.%20That%20the%20party%20is%20smarting%20from%20this%20judgment%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20mocking%20remarks%20that%20today%2C%20even%20if%20Sudama%20were%20to%20give%20some%20rice%20to%20Krishna%2C%20someone%20would%20file%20a%20PIL%20and%20the%20court%20would%20strike%20it%20down!%20Even%20the%20brazen%20retaliation%20of%20blocking%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20the%20Congress%20two%20days%20later%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20in%20a%20short%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeat-sharing%20among%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20is%20not%20the%20failure%20that%20the%20bought-out%20media%20would%20have%20us%20believe.%20It%20is%20proceeding%20apace%20and%20has%20been%20hammered%20out%20in%20UP%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20appears%20likely%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Goa.%20The%20decision%20to%20go%20their%20separate%20ways%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%20makes%20sense%20tactically%20as%20it%20will%20split%20the%20anti-incumbency%20votes.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20convince%20you%20otherwise%20with%20their%20slanted%20coverage%20and%20Mood%20Of%20The%20Nation%20polls.%20They%20reflect%20more%20the%20moods%20of%20Mr%20Adani%20and%20Aroon%20Purie%20than%20that%20of%20the%20common%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revived%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20is%20bad%20news%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20too%2C%20and%20will%20become%20even%20worse%20if%20violence%20ensues%2C%20as%20appears%20likely%2C%20given%20that%20the%20government%20has%20learned%20no%20lessons%20from%20the%202021%20agitation.%20Its%20reliance%20on%20brute%20force%20as%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20protests%20cannot%20deliver%20forever%2C%20and%20the%20people%20are%20beginning%20to%20recognise%20it%20for%20the%20tyrannical%20regime%20it%20is.%20There%20is%20widespread%20sympathy%20for%20the%20farmers%20this%20time%2C%20except%20perhaps%20among%20the%20pampered%20elites%20of%20Delhi%20who%20do%20not%20even%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20MSP%20and%20MRP%2C%20and%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20bothered%20so%20long%20as%20their%20Zomato%20delivery%20arrives%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fbusting-the-misconceived-criticisms-around-an-msp-law%5C%22%3EBusting%20the%20Misconceived%20Criticisms%20of%20an%20MSP%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20febrile%20actions%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%20also%20do%20not%20demonstrate%20that%20it%20is%20acting%20from%20a%20position%20of%20confidence.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20they%20display%20a%20certain%20desperation%20and%20nervousness.%20The%20frantic%20campaign%20to%20engineer%20defections%20of%20all%20and%20sundry%20have%20degraded%20the%20BJP%20from%20a%20washing%20machine%20to%20a%20garbage%20bin.%20It%20is%20now%20collecting%20all%20kinds%20of%20trash%20from%20other%20parties%2C%20people%20it%20branded%20as%20corrupt%20repeatedly%2C%20including%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3EAjit%20Pawar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fashok-chavan-adarsh-scam-congress-bjp%5C%22%3EAshok%20Chavan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVery%20soon%2C%20having%20collected%20all%20the%20rubbish%20from%20other%20parties%2C%20it%20will%20become%20a%20patchwork%20quilt%20of%20opportunists%20and%20lose%20its%20strong%20ideological%20character.%20According%20to%20an%20analysis%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20digital%20platform%2C%20Knocking%20News%2C%20out%20of%20303%20MPs%20in%20the%20party%2C%20only%20134%20are%20original%20BJP%20types%2C%20the%20rest%20are%20all%20imports%20from%20other%20parties.%20It%20is%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%9CCongress%20yukt%E2%80%9D%20party%20in%20rapid%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fear%20of%20losing%20is%20prompting%20other%20knee%20jerk%20reactions%3A%20the%20constant%20targeting%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20BJY-2%20(which%20was%20not%20the%20case%20in%20BJY-1)%2C%20the%20resumed%20personal%20attacks%20on%20him%20and%20his%20family%2C%20the%20renewed%20attempts%20at%20polarised%20violence%20in%20Haldwani%2C%20the%20frantic%20rush%20to%20introduce%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftalking-uniform-civil-code%5C%22%3EUniform%20Civil%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states%2C%20the%20raising%20of%20the%20spectre%20of%20CAA%20and%20NRC%20by%20the%20home%20Minister%20again%2C%20the%20reported%20deactivation%20of%20Aadhaar%20cards%20as%20alleged%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20wholesale%20conferment%20of%20Bharat%20Ratnas%20in%20order%20to%20appropriate%20the%20memory%20of%20dead%20legends%20even%20as%20the%20party%20spurns%20all%20that%20they%20stood%20for.%20The%20list%20goes%20on%2C%20but%20it%20indicates%20one%20thing%2C%20as%20surely%20as%20the%20mayoral%20elections%20in%20Chandigarh%20indicated%20brazen%20rigging%20of%20votes%3A%20that%20these%20are%20not%20the%20actions%20of%20a%20party%20confident%20of%20not%20only%20a%20victory%2C%20but%20of%20a%20two-third%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20be%20facing%20a%20reality%20check%2C%20finally%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%20is%20committing%20one%20blunder%20after%20another.%20With%20each%20such%20fiasco%2C%20it%20is%20denting%20its%20image%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20election%20narrative%20this%20time%20sounds%20decidedly%20hollow%20and%20devoid%20of%20any%20substance.%20It%20offers%20nothing%20but%20the%20three%20M%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20Mandir%2C%20Masjid%20and%20Muslim%20%E2%80%93%20a%20refrain%20which%20is%20beginning%20to%20sound%20jaded%20and%20repetitive.%20Real%20economic%20improvement%20has%20bypassed%2090%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20this%20shows%20in%20just%20about%20every%20human%20development%20matrix.%20The%20so-called%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cguarantees%E2%80%9D%20are%20nothing%20but%20discredited%20%3Cem%3Ejumlas%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20cosmetic%20plastic%20surgery.%20So%2C%20one%20comes%20back%20to%20the%20question%20one%20posed%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20piece%3A%20What%20makes%20the%20BJP%20so%20confident%20of%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20spite%20of%20all%20these%20adverse%20indications%20%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clues%2C%20perhaps%2C%20are%20to%20be%20found%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20ground%20is%20being%20prepared%3A%20the%20constant%20refrain%20of%20400%2B%20seats%2C%20the%20slanted%20pre-poll%20surveys%20endorsing%20these%20estimates%2C%20and%20the%20amplification%20of%20these%20predictions%20by%20an%20obliging%20media.%20So%20that%20when%20the%20400%2B%20is%20declared%20after%20the%20polling%2C%20people%20would%20not%20question%20it%20because%20they%20had%20already%20been%20pre-conditioned%20to%20expect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20it%20be%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20joker%20up%20its%20sleeve%3F%20The%20EVMs%2C%20perhaps%3F%20A%20national%20roll-out%20of%20the%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20model%2C%20under%20the%20benevolent%20gaze%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%20But%20I%20am%20reminded%20of%20that%20intriguing%20quote%20from%20Arthur%20Conan%20Doyle%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20have%20eliminated%20all%20which%20is%20impossible%2C%20then%20whatever%20remains%2C%20however%20improbable%2C%20must%20be%20the%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20it.%20And%20worry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favayshukla.blogspot.com%2F2023%2F12%2Ffake-democracies-and-real-ones.html%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20blog%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EView%20from%20%5BGreater%5D%20Kailash%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17