a.com%2F%3Fp%3D343042%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20a%20visit%20to%20Nagpur's%20open%20science%20parks%2C%20IAS%20officer%20Vivek%20Johnson%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20build%20such%20amenities%20for%20the%20students%20of%20Chandrapur%20district%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20hopes%20of%20instilling%20a%20love%20for%20science%20and%20play%20in%20them.%20Here's%20his%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343042%2Fias-vivek-johnson-establishes-open-science-parks-sports-complexes-for-rural-children-transforms-chandrapur-maharashtra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mirwaiz%20Farooq%20Appointed%20to%20the%20Panel%20of%20Islamic%20Jurists%20on%20Crescent%20Sighting%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23173520%2FFotoJet-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20fasting%20less%20than%20a%20fortnight%20away%2C%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chairman%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%20has%20been%20appointed%20to%20an%20advisory%20committee%20of%20top%20Islamic%20jurists%20and%20other%20religious%20leaders%20and%20scholars%20who%20will%20take%20the%20final%20call%20on%20the%20vexed%20issue%20of%20crescent%20sighting%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-level%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20local%20administration%20is%20facing%20accusations%20of%20making%20attempts%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20religious%20practices%20of%20Kashmiri%20Muslims%20following%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20when%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party-led%20Union%20government%20took%20direct%20charge%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday%20(February%2022)%2C%20Mufti%20Nasir-ul-Islam%2C%20the%20Grand%20Mufti%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20after%20gathering%20testimonies%20from%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20and%20Ruet-e-Hilal%20Committee%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20official%20crescent%20sighting%20grouping%2C%20the%20ten-member%20advisory%20committee%20shall%20be%20consulted%20before%20making%20any%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Mirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20designation%20in%20the%20committee%20has%20not%20been%20specified%2C%20his%20name%20figures%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20of%20its%20ten%20members%20which%20also%20includes%20Maulvi%20Rehmatullah%20Mir%20Qasmi%2C%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(MPLB)%2C%20and%20MPLB%20vice-president%2C%20Syed%20Aslam%20Andrabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20MPLB%20appointed%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Ladakh%20for%20giving%20testimonies%20about%20the%20possible%20sighting%20of%20the%20crescent%2C%20will%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Grand%20Mufti%20on%20March%2010%20when%20the%20lunar%20month%20of%20Ramzan%20is%20expected%20to%20start%20in%20India%20and%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ramzan%2C%20Muslims%20observe%20dawn-to-dusk%20fast%20for%2029%20or%2030%20days%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20rotation%20(or%20age)%20around%20the%20earth%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20each%20Islamic%20day%20begins%20at%20sunset%2C%20credible%20testimonies%20about%20the%20sighting%20of%20the%20crescent%20at%20dusk%20are%20mandatory%20for%20religious%20leaders%20to%20announce%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20month%20of%20Ramzan%20and%20also%20Shawwal%2C%20the%20tenth%20lunar%20month%20that%20follows%20and%20whose%20first%20day%20is%20celebrated%20as%20the%20Eid-ul-Fitr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20any%20witness%20(Ruet)%20is%20received%2C%20the%20members%20are%20supposed%20to%20testify%20its%20reliability%20and%20if%20deemed%20true%20are%20to%20accordingly%20share%20and%20convey%20it%20to%20the%20Grand%20Mufti%2C%20or%20to%20any%20member%20of%20the%20constituted%20committee%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20committee%20will%20%E2%80%9Cdiscuss%20the%20reliability%20of%20witnesses%20before%20making%20the%20final%20announcement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20official%20crescent%20sighting%20committee%20is%20a%20poorly-serviced%20team%20which%20lacks%20the%20scientific%20and%20technical%20wherewithal%20to%20sight%20the%20crescent%2C%20making%20it%20dependent%20on%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20official%20moon%20sighting%20committee%20and%20also%20causing%20a%20dent%20in%20its%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20wants%20to%20decouple%20the%20decades-old%20tradition%2C%20wherein%20people%20from%20Kashmir%20celebrate%20Eid%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20because%20of%20its%20political%20connotations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMufti%20Nazir%20Qasmi%2C%20a%20noted%20Islamic%20scholar%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20sighting%20the%20crescent%20is%20difficult%20in%20Kashmir%20because%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20peculiar%20weather%20conditions%20that%20make%20clouds%20a%20persistent%20feature%20of%20skies%20during%20the%20year%20and%20especially%20in%20the%20winter%20months%20from%20November%20to%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Muslims%20in%20our%20neighbourhood%20announce%20the%20sighting%20of%20the%20Eid%20crescent%2C%20we%20are%20also%20obliged%20under%20the%20Shariah%20(Islamic)%20law%20to%20celebrate%20the%20Eid%20along%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mufti%20Qasmi%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Islamic%20jurisprudence%20wing%20at%20the%20Bandipora%20seminary%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20after%20a%20bitter%20face-off%20with%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20ulema%20and%20other%20religious%20leaders%20over%20the%20alleged%20attempts%20to%20politicise%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20crescent%20sighting%2C%20the%20Wakf%20board%2C%20which%20is%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20major%20shrines%20and%20mosques%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20had%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20set%20up%20its%20own%20Ruet-e-Hilal%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wakf%20board%20has%20also%20faced%20criticism%20for%20allegedly%20taking%20control%20of%20some%20Muslim%20Sufi%20shrines%20in%20Kashmir%20which%20were%20under%20the%20management%20of%20local%20bodies%2C%20prompting%20some%20custodians%20of%20these%20shrines%20to%20knock%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20Wakf%20Board%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Darakshan%20Andrabi%2C%20was%20snubbed%20by%20Maulvi%20Qasmi%2C%20who%20is%20part%20of%20the%20new%20advisory%20committee%20on%20crescent%20sighting%2C%20for%20allegedly%20interfering%20in%20what%20he%20said%20were%20%E2%80%9Cstrictly%20religious%20matters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20the%20National%20Investigations%20Agency%20had%20raided%20Maulvi%20Qasmi%2C%20who%20heads%20Dar-Ul-Uloom%20Raheemiya%2C%20Kashmir%20largest%20Islamic%20seminary%20situated%20in%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Bandipora%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20terror%20radicalisation%20case%20soon%20after%20his%20comments%20on%20Andrabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mirwaiz%20was%20disallowed%20from%20coming%20out%20of%20his%20house%20and%20leading%20the%20congregational%20Friday%20prayers%20at%20the%20Jamia%20Masjid%2C%20an%20official%20of%20Anjuman%20Auqaf%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%20historic%20shrine%C2%A0%C2%A0in%20Srinagar%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20a%20hostile%20attitude%20of%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20not%20only%20sad%20but%20also%20causes%20great%20grief%20among%20the%20people%20here.%20This%20undue%20interference%20in%20religious%20a