20terrain%20playing%20spoilsport.%20But%20once%20you%20reach%20Kundan%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20all%20discomfort%20is%20washed%20away%20by%20the%20warm%20soup%2C%20prepared%20and%20served%20by%20his%20wife%20Kala%20as%20a%20welcome%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smiling%20couple%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20in%20their%20forties%20%E2%80%94%20will%20unleash%20their%20hospitality%20upon%20your%20arrival.%20They%20will%20waste%20no%20time%20in%20telling%20you%20that%20this%20is%20your%20home%20and%20you%20must%20make%20yourself%20feel%20at%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20evening%20and%20Kundan%20will%20urge%20you%20to%20share%20stories%20of%20your%20culture%2C%20while%20he%20shares%20some%20of%20his%20own.%20Throughout%20your%20stay%2C%20the%20couple%20will%20encourage%20you%20to%20eat%2C%20feast%2C%20and%20eat%20some%20more!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lived%20off%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduce%20of%20their%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20decades%20now%2C%20Kundan%20has%20an%20ardent%20respect%20for%20the%20two%20bighas%20of%20land.%20The%20vivid%20colours%20of%20brown%20(wheat)%2C%20red%20(apples)%2C%20and%20green%20(pulses)%2C%20interspersed%20with%20blues%2C%20oranges%2C%20and%20yellows%20will%20compete%20for%20your%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-10-at-6.23.03-PM-1-1708690468.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kundan%20Singh%20and%20his%20wife%20Kala%20with%20their%20guests%20at%20the%20Kundan%20Homestay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024