a-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Currently%2C%20his%20innovation%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20is%20installed%20in%2018%20hospitals.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20design%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20lotus%20or%20a%20crown.%20Just%20like%20they%20can%20be%20entirely%20closed%2C%20our%20cap%20is%20wrapped%20around%20the%20head%20of%20the%20patient%2C%20and%20the%20cap%20can%20be%20adjusted%20using%20the%20velcro%20as%20per%20the%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuveer%20informs%20that%20a%20patient%20needs%20to%20wear%20this%20cap%2030%20minutes%20before%20the%20chemotherapy%20infusion%2C%20during%20chemotherapy%20infusion%2C%20and%20between%2030%20minutes%20and%20two%20hours%20post-chemotherapy.%20The%20device%20reduces%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20scalp%20from%2035%20to%2016%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20on%20the%20device%2C%20Raghuveer%20also%20focussed%20on%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20device.%20%E2%80%9COur%20competitors%20charge%20about%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20for%20their%20device.%20We%20reduced%20the%20cost%20drastically%20so%20that%20patients%20in%20developing%20countries%20could%20also%20afford%20this%20care.%20Hospitals%20can%20buy%20our%20device%20for%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2016%20lakh%20depending